      <section id="bur-oak">
        <h2>Bur Oak</h2>
        <img
          src="https://www.shutterstock.com/image-photo/majestic-burr-oak-tree-grassy-600nw-2372732621.jpg"
          alt="Bur Oak Tree"
        />
        <div class="info">
          <h3>Planting</h3>
          <p>
            The Bur Oak is a hardy tree that thrives in a range of soil types.
            It's best to plant in well-drained soil with full sun exposure.
          </p>
          <h3>Care</h3>
          <p>
            Water regularly during the first few years of growth. Once
            established, Bur Oaks are drought-tolerant. Prune during the dormant
            season to maintain shape.
          </p>
        </div>
      </section>
    </main>

